Program: The Reith Lectures
Title: The Body Beautiful
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00c5j0d
Last Broadcast Date: Sat 28 Jun 2008
Chinese Vistas: Jonathan Spence lectures about China. Recorded at Lord's cricket ground. Spence discusses how Chinese ideas of sport and athleticism have slowly evolved over the centuries, from languorous courtship and formalised martial arts to the demanding arenas of team sports and the ultimate Olympic challenges that China will controversially host in August. Show less